  <brief_title>Omega 3 Lipid Emulsions and Liver Transplantation</brief_title>
  <acronym>OTLT</acronym>
  <official_title>Impact of Pre-treatment of Living-donor Liver Transplant Recipients With Omega 3 Enriched Lipid Emulsions on Graft and Patient Outcome. A Prospective, Randomized, Multi-central Trial.</official_title>
