  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study Aims to investigate the possible benfecial impact of Omega 3 containing lipid
      emulsions on recepients for living donor liver transplantation. both perioperative and
      postoperative application of the study treatment are tested to determine the best time for
      drug adminstration.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
